@* Root component: a toggle button and a root-level @if, no wrapping element. The
   conditional's branch mounts and unmounts directly against #app (mount()'s target) --
   #77's third false positive, closed by decision 89. The button sibling emits in source
   order before the conditional's comment anchor.

   No whitespace between </button> and @if, matching If.razor's contract: Razor turns
   SOURCE whitespace between sibling nodes into text nodes, and there is none here. *@

<button id="toggle" @onclick="Toggle">toggle</button>@if (show)
{
    <span id="cond">visible</span>
}

@code {
    private bool show = true;
    void Toggle() { show = !show; }
}
